Description: Number of data set that was active when amovement was interrupted.When a movement is interrupted, the number ofthe data set that was being processed at the pointin time of the interruption is contained in thisparameter.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 302D:BhModbus 11542Profibus 11542CIP 145.1.11ModbusTCP 11542EtherCAT 302D:BhPROFINET 11542
